00:15:19.760 --> 00:15:20.880
Anda pergi sendirian?

00:15:22.800 --> 00:15:23.880
Tetapi dimana?

00:15:24.480 --> 00:15:28.400
Tahukah Anda Hotel
Salt Lake Internasional?

00:15:29.080 --> 00:15:32.840
Saya pergi ke sana.
